text: Framly Nainggolan (born in Jakarta, Indonesia, July 29, 1984) is an actor from Indonesia. He played in several movies such as Jenglot Pantai Selatan (2011). He is the winner of the competition of L-Men Of The Year 2005. == Filmography == * Jenglot Pantai Selatan (2011) == References == == Other websites == * Profile at Indonesianfilmcenter.com Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Jakarta
